<p>'So proud of my daughter Gussie. She is a healthcare worker working with people who have disabilities,' he wrote, alongside a selfie of Augusta in personal protective equipment.  </p>

<p>Phoebe previously shared an old happy snap of her parents in their youth.</p>

<p>'Stumbled across this pic of JJ and Deano whilst cleaning out the shed,' she wrote.</p>

<p>The Instagram post included the captions 'romantic picnic' and 'good thinking Deano'.  </p>

